###
Ancient Debris will now drop 1 to 3 netherite scraps
###
on mine:
    if event-block = ancient debris:
        cancel item drops
        drop (random integer between 1 and 3) of netherite scrap at event-block
    if event-block is diamond ore or deepslate diamond ore:
        cancel item drops
        drop (random integer between 1 and 3) of diamonds at event-block